DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to study Non-Invasive Performance evaluation of monitoring algorithm.
DOC.brief_title: Novel Non-Invasive Monitoring Parameter in Healthy Volunteers
DOC.detailed_description: Assess equivalency, performance, and accuracy of a new monitoring algorithm in Healthy Volunteers.
DOC.criteria: Subject is 18 or older Subject is willing and able to provide written consent Severe contact allergies to standard adhesive materials Subjects with abnormalities that may prevent proper application of the device Women who are pregnant or lactating Subjects with significant Arrhythmias
